626
00:36:01,466 --> 00:36:03,210
syndrome de Fitz Hugh Curtis ?

627
00:36:03,556 --> 00:36:05,242
Encore la gonorrhée ?

628
00:36:05,396 --> 00:36:07,033
Vous avez mieux ?

629
00:36:07,387 --> 00:36:10,412
Testez-la.
